title: It's All Zeit 2/4: Shannen Doherty, Chasten Buttigieg, Knicks, McMillions, Iowa Caucus
itunes:title: It's All Zeit 2/4: Shannen Doherty, Chasten Buttigieg, Knicks, McMillions, Iowa Caucus
description:
On this edition of It's All Zeit Jack and Miles discuss how Shannen Doherty announces her cancer has returned, Chasten Buttigieg claps back at the bigoted person who withdrew her vote for Pete, the Knicks fire their president, the new McDonald's documentary, and the Iowa Caucus is happening...sort of.
